node.text:
Discovering underwater history in Norway, Aqaba, Egypt and Malta. Tag someone who needs to see this! 🤯 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on nomadfervor.com (link in my bio: @nomadfervor) 

Locations:
1. S/S Frankenwald near Gulen, Norway
2, 5, 6, 7, 9, 10. Aqaba, Jordan
3. The P31 from Comino in Malta
4. The Giannis D at Abu Nuhas, Red Sea, Egypt
8. Rozi the tug boat in Ċirkewwa near the ferry terminal to Gozo, Malta.

📷 @alex_dawson_photography

node.text:
What is the relationship between architecture and @nature? 😍 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting nomadfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @nomadfervor

Which photo is your favorite, from 1 to 10?

Save this post If you're planning to explore Iran for the most spectacular spots to visit! 📝

𝟭𝟬 𝗕𝗲𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗶𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗔𝗿𝗰𝗵𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗰𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗮𝗹 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝘃𝗲𝗹𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝗜𝗿𝗮𝗻
1. Imam Reza Holy Shrine
2. Nasir al Molk Mosque
3. Mollabashi Historical House
4. Hazrat Masumeh Holy Shrine
5. Nasir al Molk Mosque
6. National Arts Museum, Tehran
7. Shah Mosque
8. Sadoughi House Yazd
9. Jameh Mosque of Shafei
10. Borujerdiha Historical House

📸 @amir.hossein.mirmoeini
📍 Iran
